The paper deals with face recognition, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed Deep Comparator Network (DCN) is a neural network architecture, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions image retrieval, which is a subfield of multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
